=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_QuadL_ex2 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 1838 Hz, featuring punchy attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 1837.9174
  harmonic_decay_rate: -6.4973
  harmonic_regularity: 0.2945
  pitch_clarity: 10.8356
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -25.5107
  resonance_freq: 3509.9121

